<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>string on 南寨小子</title><link>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/tags/string/</link><description>Recent content in string on 南寨小子</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://kangxiaoning.github.io/tags/string/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Golang String and slice</title><link>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/post/2021/01/string-and-slice/</link><pubDate>Thu, 21 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/post/2021/01/string-and-slice/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;code>Golang&lt;/code>里的&lt;code>string&lt;/code>和&lt;code>slice&lt;/code>都属于&lt;code>reference type&lt;/code>，即这种类型会有一个指针，指向&lt;code>underlying&lt;/code>的数据结构，在copy这种类型时只是对他的header进行copy，并不会copy真正存储的数据，从而达到共用内存，提升效率的目的。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>